{"tid":1569261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［光復香港 時代革命］全民警棍時代降臨？裝假狗！","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:56:05.000Z","uid":199631,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2a79f3c95cc257c83153a268d317069d0bfab2","tid":1569261,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"既然而家休班警隨身都有警棍，咁不如全民都扮狗，俾大眾市民了解而家香港狗賊<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1）只恐嚇 不傷害</span></strong></span><br />\n而家仲有啲掛住返工返學嘅中立人士，係佢地返工果時無啦啦嚇9佢，話係休班狗，係佢地面前拎住棍周圍揚，俾大家睇下平時班狗點對啲手足。記住不傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2）成群結隊扮狗 唔好單機</span></strong></span><br />\n到時真狗埋泥走唔切 而且人多好辦事 互相照應 當然要練下 唔好變左人多手腳亂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3）見到藍屍</span></strong></span><br />\n佢地可能會幫你 嚇埋佢一份 嚇到佢都唔敢講野 目的係全民反狗<br />\n<br />\n咁岩上網睇到有個自稱休班狗而且拎住警棍周圍揚，細心啲諗 都唔知真狗定手足裝假狗 忽發奇想 梗係要發揚光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中秋快樂 香港人<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"2cda17085fc7527e85215d773237c7bf66038786","tid":1569261,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"054f2a8b235f16bf438156aaaa4c5ee4f40ffc2f","tid":1569261,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21f3a4e413b530aeb6b7985e2fffb2908a4bbc8e","tid":15692